{"tid":1920214,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［集思廣益］東薈城電梯到底可以點樣活化呢？","createTime":"2020-03-11T10:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T19:23:36.000Z","uid":271359,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"90138dcdc9d95089340319a56c43148a0b153b86","tid":1920214,"uid":271359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"【千奇百趣的電梯】<br />\n<br />\n在很多本地旅遊雜誌的介紹中<br />\n提到東涌都是「昂坪360」丶「天壇大佛」丶「迪士尼樂園」為特色<br />\n<br />\n作為一個20多年的東涌街坊<br />\n除了「羅馬」和「金牛」，還有「舊碼」或123號外<br />\n我會形容這條電梯是東涌人的集體回憶<br />\n雖然是千篇一律的建築物<br />\n但街坊對於它的看法也是個神秘的謎<br />\n因為東薈城很久都沒有使用它<br />\n<br />\n在幾年前起至今<br />\n我都會去信或致電詢問電梯狀況<br />\n直至上個月，東薈城代表回覆<br />\n這條電梯因為颱風的理由及日久失修<br />\n所以暫定永久關閉<br />\n<br />\n我希望在此徵詢大家的意見<br />\n如果街坊們對電梯的活化和用途有新穎的想法<br />\n都可以提出，我會相約東薈城代表詳談<br />\n謝謝大家😁<br />\n<br />\n---------------<br />\nInstagram : w.c.yeung<br />\nfacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/SheepWongChunYeung/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FSheepWongChunYeung%2F&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=76cdeca8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/SheepWongChunYeung/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WpMcg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WpMcg8.jpg&h=0693cb22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101197744629082/posts/193944755354380/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101197744629082%2Fposts%2F193944755354380%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=b5PQnn7rv2nSxMH%2F6z0stnGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=db0969a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101197744629082/posts/193944755354380/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"c82a38dd82eee4155963193ddc9f0b4b03ee8a6e","tid":1920214,"uid":2377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T10:13:25.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f610323e3387e3ddab23ff68ac877b7c7ad3182c","tid":1920214,"uid":2377,"like":0,"d